<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Event Cancelled: {{eventName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
      background-color: #f8d7da; 
      margin: 0; 
      padding: 0; 
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 20px auto; 
      padding: 20px; 
      background: #fff; 
      border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; 
      border-radius: 5px; 
    }
    .header { 
      background-color: #dc3545; 
      color: #fff; 
      padding: 10px; 
      text-align: center; 
    }
    .content { 
      margin: 20px 0; 
      font-size: 16px; 
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
    }
    .footer { 
      font-size: 12px; 
      color: #721c24; 
      text-align: center; 
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Event Cancelled</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>We regret to inform you that the event <strong>{{eventName}}</strong> you registered for has been cancelled.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact the event organizers for further details.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The PASA Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
